# 12. Firewall (iptables)

Install:

```
apt install iptables
```

List rules:

```
iptables -L
```

Insert rule:

```
iptables -I OUTPUT -p tcp -d 172.16.238.100 --dport 443 -j ACCEPT
```

Delete rule:

```
iptables -D OUTPUT 5
```

Rules are processed top to bottom.

